      "rationale": "Scoped out per MRL 2 assessment plan. Sensitivity of hemolysis index to inlet turbulence intensity (range 1–10%) evaluated informally: RH variation of ±4.3% across the range, within overall model uncertainty budget. Formal uncertainty quantification not required at this model risk level."
    },
