      "rationale": "One pump specimen fabricated to nominal drawing dimensions used for all validation experiments. Unit-to-unit geometric variability not characterized. Acceptable at MRL 2 given that the COU addresses nominal design performance; manufacturing tolerance sensitivity addressed separately via parametric CFD sweep."
