      "rationale": "Blood analogue (40% glycerin-water) used in validation experiments; clinical blood used in COU application. Viscosity equivalency within 8% across shear rate range 100–1000 s-1. Non-Newtonian effects at low shear rates not captured by analogue fluid; acknowledged as limitation within acceptable bounds for MRL 2 assessment."
